### Upload video and start dubbing job
POST http://localhost:8000/api/jobs
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="target_lang"

Spanish
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source_lang"

English
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./test.mp4
--boundary--

### List all jobs
GET http://localhost:8000/api/jobs

### Get job details
GET http://localhost:8000/api/jobs/{{job_id}}

### Stream job progress (SSE)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/jobs/{{job_id}}/events
Accept: text/event-stream

### Download dubbed video
GET http://localhost:8000/api/jobs/{{job_id}}/output

### Delete a job
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/jobs/{{job_id}}